Relive the era of profound love and deep emotions with Alka Yagnik & Udit Narayan's timeless track 'Kitni Bechain Hoke' from the famous movie, 'Kasoor'. Immerse yourself in the enchanting melodies that blend seamlessly with the theme of sensual romance. Allow this compelling song to take you on a nostalgic trip back to 2001, when love songs touched the heart and soul. Let the warmth of the lyrics fill your heart.
 
Kitni Bechain Hoke

Song: Kitni Bechain Hoke
Album: Kasoor
Artist: Alka Yagnik | Udit Narayan
Music Director: Nadeem-Shravan
Lyricist: Sameer 


Experience the charm of love once again. Share your favorite stanza from the song in the comment section below and don't forget to subscribe our channel for more timeless classics from Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan. Here's to letting the magic of music continue to live on, inspiring a sense of love and romanticism that stands the test of time!

snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Pre-Release Event Announcement Trailer | Rishab Shetty | NTR | ShreyasMedia
snippet.description:
Watch Kantara Chapter 1 Pre-Release Event Announcement Trailer on #ShreyasMedia 


#KantaraChapter1PreReleaseEvent #AnnouncementTrailer
#KantaraChapter1 #RishabShetty #Kantara #ALegend #DivineEpic #VijayKiragandu #AjaneeshLoknath #RukminiVasanth #GulshanDevaiah #Jayaram #KantaraTrailer #KantaraChapter1Trailer #Kantarachapter1onOct2 #KantaraTeluguTrailer #KantaraChapter1TeluguTrailer 

The makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies, and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025. 

Movie Credits-

snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | New Trailer
snippet.description:
This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don‚Äôt miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With ‚ÄúAvatar: Fire and Ash,‚Äù James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na‚Äôvi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na‚Äôvi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Salda√±a), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

snippet.title: VALORANT Champions Paris ‚Äî Playoffs Stage ‚Äî Day 15
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world‚Äôs top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We‚Äôre proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ValorantEsports
Photos from the Event: https://www.flickr.com/photos/valorantesports/
Official VALORANT Esports News: https://valorantesports.com/news
Web: https://valorantesports.com

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion üèÜüî• Live Reaction üò≥
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fire‚Äôs history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And let‚Äôs not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today
